    "content" : "Hi FB - Going to do my valve clearances in the next couple of months. Do you use sealant or just good quality cork gaskets ? I’ve heard a school of thought to use sealant on the cover side only, due to different expansion rates do the heads and the covers, but would prefer to use gaskets only if I can.",
