    "content" : "They changed from 0.04 to 0.06 due to the smaller setting causing burnt exhaust valves - particularly on No.3\n<br> The factory increased it to 0.06 to give a bit more clearance and tolerance on the valves.\n<br> You can run 0.04 but be very careful with frequency of gap checks and note if any keep going tight - this means the valve is stretching.",
